{"books":[{"id":"rmrb","name":"人民日报","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"","files":[],"article":{"title":"红旗颂——献给建国十五周年","authors":["张志民"],"dates":[{"year":1964,"month":10,"day":5}],"is_range_date":false,"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗颂"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——献给建国十五周年"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"张志民"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十月的水呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十月的山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十月的蓝天啊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——海一样的蓝。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迷人啊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"宝石哪有蓝天美？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"豁朗啊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五洲四海在眼前。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看呵！看东海，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"秋汛催帆千舱满，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望呵！望中原，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"棉垛如云啊谷成山！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"指北国呵！数江南，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命胸襟，比天宽！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"草原的羊群啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高天的雁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大路上的马儿啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"长江的船，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十月的天啊，十月的天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十月的风光"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——瞧不完。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"若问我最爱哪一景？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我爱那——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万杆红旗卷蓝天……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"二"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗劈天呵"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——天门开！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万杆红旗举天来！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"染千村，照万寨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看啊！看红旗的怒浪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万马飞腾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——天鼓碎！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千里奔雷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——泰山歪！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三山晃动五岭摇呵！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"万丈波涛"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——盖山海！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看！那是多少路大军呵！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"重重红旗重重浪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千年古道今日窄！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看！那是多少旗手呵！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从血泊里爬起的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"身上的血迹"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——还没顾揩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从牢房里冲出的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"脖颈上的锁链，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——还没砸开！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗呵，红旗！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗路上战鼓催，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗呼啦"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——卷千载！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前进，马不停蹄，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少道闸门啊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——等我们开！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前进！人不下鞍，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——天下还有半边黑！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪里有闲情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去叙那些才子佳人的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——朝朝暮暮，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪里有工夫"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去讲那些帝王将相的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——兴兴衰衰！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"讲吧，兄弟，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"讲革命红旗哪里来？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"讲井冈山红浪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是如何染红赣江水？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"讲南京的石城，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是怎么打开？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"讲金沙江畔、大渡河旁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是多少英雄的旗手呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在战斗里呼喊："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——“人在红旗在！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"讲血染的红花岗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它是怎么样"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"变作了广州的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——“雨花台”……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"讲吧！安源的老矿工！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"讲你怎么样"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挺着被打断的腰杆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把革命的红旗插上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——镐车架？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"讲吧！佃户的儿子，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"讲你怎么样"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从父亲的尸首前，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把那染血的红旗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——接过来……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"三"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗呵，红旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我身生在红旗下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"最美的歌儿啊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——唱给你！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗啊，红旗！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要画出你的英姿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我该用——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎样的生花妙笔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗呵，红旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要赞颂你的光辉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我该用——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"怎样壮丽的诗句？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“庄严”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——显得太轻，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“崇高”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——显得太低！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗呵！红旗！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我只能用自己"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个劳动者的语言，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"来比喻你的形象："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你，铺开来是我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——辽阔的天地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你，站在那里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是站立着我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——一个伟大的阶级！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗，在大路上行进，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗，在蓝天里高举！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"党呵——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们无产阶级的先锋队。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"组成你英雄的行列，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是多少啊——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们最优秀的儿女！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席呵——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们最伟大的旗手！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是你，是你呵！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"挺身在——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战斗的最前列！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"手撑着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——我们的大旗！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"风暴！是那样险恶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"道路！是那样崎岖！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每一步路上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都是关山叠叠，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——荆棘遍地！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"攀登每一步梯阶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都要挺走千尺巉岩，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——顶着漫天风雨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"可是我们啊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们要高喊一万声"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——不怕！不怕！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"因为我们有"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——革命的红旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们有党，有毛主席！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席呀，毛主席！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们生活在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你光辉的时代，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"浑身都披满了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士的骄傲啊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"毛主席呀，毛主席！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们每一片"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"幸福的情思里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都包含着你伟大的名字，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们欢呼着你，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是欢呼着胜利！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你的每一句话啊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都给予了我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——翻天的力气！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"嘉陵江上的纤夫啊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"黄浦滩上的苦力！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拉萨河畔的朗生啊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大凉山的奴隶……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站起来了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——在红旗下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗下站起人六亿！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六亿人啊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六亿人行进在大路上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六亿人啊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"六亿人紧贴着毛主席，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"同一个步伐，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"共一个志气！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是这样的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千万双黑手啊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"筑起了我们——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"人民共和国的大堤！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五年、十年、"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——十五年！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一个世纪的六分之一。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十五年啊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是多么暂短的一瞬啊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在历史的长流里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只能算作是"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——一朵浪花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"但就是这朵浪花呀！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它开放得"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是那么样的雄伟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——神奇！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十五年呵！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十五年换了天和地！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十五年呵！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千年血泪成过去！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"海盗们——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用一块钢锭"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就要把我们压扁的时代，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"过去了，过去了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看！鞍钢的炉火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"映红了天际！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"殖民者——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"用一滴洋油"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就要我们屈膝的日子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"过去了，永远过去了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看！那数不尽的油塔，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正挺着胸脯，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从我们的国土上站起！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"过去了，过去了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"任人践踏的时代"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——过去了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拔锅顶债的日子"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——过去了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"什么叫作“弃儿卖女”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们年轻的母亲，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将再也不能理解"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这句话的分量，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"什么叫作“骨肉分离”？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的第二代"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只有从历史教科书上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"才能查得出"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——它的定义！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十五年呵！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十五年换了天和地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十五年呵！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十五年掀开了个新世纪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看！十五岁的红领巾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——一片初升的朝阳，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正行进在"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"进军的行列里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看！十五年的花果，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在祖国的大地上，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"已变得万紫千红"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"化作了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——满园桃李！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这就是我们的今天啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看天，天有情，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看地，地有意！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"祖国啊，祖国！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当我在机床厂的车间"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抚摸着那一台台"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——乌亮的机器；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当我在人民公社"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一眼无边的稻海里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"遍数那一面面"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——丰产红旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"又怎么能止得住"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那夺眶的热泪呢！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流吧，流吧！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为着我们的今天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——我们辉煌的业绩"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"也为着我们的昨日"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——饥寒交迫的奴隶……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"四"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗，在蓝天里飞飘，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"进军的行列啊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"象烈火，象海潮！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大路——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命的大路呵！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"它可并不是鸟语花香的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——林荫小道，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是一条"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——战斗的道路呵！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在这条大路上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有一处"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——不滚荡着战火，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"弥漫着烟硝……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看！看剑花飞闪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听！听枪声呼啸！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天呵！今天还摆不得"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——庆功喜筵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今天呵！今天还奏不得"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——升平鼓乐！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的敌人"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们还并不甘心"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——交枪求饶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看，他们在狂浪里挣扎！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要抓住一块岩石"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哪怕是——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一根稻草……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看吧！看那个"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"昨日的“大掌柜”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"袖筒里藏的“变天账”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"听吧！听那个"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"往日的地主婆"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"睡梦里还在说："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“土改的大仇啊，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今生不报来世报！”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看到了吧！听到了吧！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是多少种啊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向我们进攻的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——长枪、大炮！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是多少样啊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"要砍断我们革命红旗的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——斧、锯、刀、凿……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看啊，看到了吧！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"肯尼迪——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从坟墓里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"对我们的红旗"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仍在瞪着"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——仇恨的眼睛！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看啊！看到了吧！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"蒋介石——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这个已漂荡了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"十五年的幽灵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"直到今天"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他仍在那里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——磨刀……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"资产阶级老爷们，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为诅咒——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们的红旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"每天要作一万次"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——“祈祷”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"帝国主义的帮凶，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为要扯下我们的红旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们搜尽枯肠"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——咬牙，跺脚，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"恨上帝无情"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"偏没“赐予”他们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"足以制服我们的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——“绝计”“高着”！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们，他们为什么"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那么害怕"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——我们的红旗！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把消灭红旗的计划"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"当作他们的最高梦想，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——最终目标！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不砍断我们的红旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"他们死不瞑目，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"望见一缕红霞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都让他们心惊"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——使他们肉跳！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"呵！原来——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"巴黎公社的红旗呵！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就已经试探了"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"资本主义的稳固性，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"证明了——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那个吃人的制度，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"完全可以"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——打倒！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"随之而来的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"千千万万的革命红旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"证明了，证明了啊！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"旧世界并不是一块"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"凿不透的铁板"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"只不过是一条"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——即将沉没的破船，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正在风雨中"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——飘摇……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前进呵，红旗！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前进呵，真正的革命者！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命啊——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是要翻天覆地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们啊——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"就是要把资本主义"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——葬进大海！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从我们的地球上铲掉！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看！那是谁？"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在向他们投掷"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——“救生圈”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"揪住他！揪住他！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让所有革命的人民"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都看清"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——他的嘴脸！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都认清"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——叛徒的面貌！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"革命——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这两个光辉大字，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是用纯金铸成，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"敲起来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——铿锵震响！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"站起来"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——明光闪耀！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们不允许，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"马克思的英灵不允许，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们整个的阶级"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——不允许！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不允许！不允许！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拿先驱者的鲜血，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"去换——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高跟鞋、博士帽……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"五"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗呵，红旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗在大路上"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——乘风前进！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红旗在蓝天里"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——如锦、似云，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看，看我们浩荡的大军，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一浪追着一浪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"后阵撵着前阵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跟上来了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跟上来，千千万万的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——雷锋班！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跟上来了！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"跟上来，千千万万的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——大寨人……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前进呵——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是多少面红旗呵！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在向我们招手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前进呵——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是多少面红旗呵！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在向我们问讯！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"非洲兄弟"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为我们的胜利"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——敲起了皮鼓！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"哈瓦那的母亲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"向十月的天安门"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——正挥舞着花巾"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从大同江、从红河口……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"那是多少地方，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"多少进军的行列呵，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在同我们"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——枪影交辉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"并肩前进！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"举起来呀，举起来！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把我们革命的红旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"举得更高，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——握得更紧！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"传下去呀，传下去！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"把革命的红旗，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"传给我们的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"今生儿女"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——万代子孙！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前进呵，前进！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让红旗化作遍地鲜花，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为人间大地"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——铺一条灿烂的大道！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"让红旗——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"变作漫天彩霞，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为共产主义的胜利，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"筑一座——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"顶天立地的"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"——凯旋门……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一九六四年国庆前夕。"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":1,"page_end":1,"alias":""},"tags":[{"type":"文稿类型","name":"文章"}]}]}